%^CYAN%^Psions%^RESET%^ are able to select a discipline that represents their inner nature.

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^Be aware%^RESET%^ - You can change your discipline once every three days with the 'discipline' command.

%^CYAN%^Discipline specific spells are as follows:%^RESET%^

%^CYAN%^Egoist:%^RESET%^
    thicken skin
    animal affinity
    chameleon
    deathward
    breath of life
    restoration
    lesser transformation
    shadow double
    shadow body

%^CYAN%^Seer:%^RESET%^ 
    dissonance
    clairvoyance
    hypercognition
    escape detection
    remote viewing
    legend lore
    prying eyes
    fortune fate
    foresight

%^CYAN%^Shaper:%^RESET%^ 
    minor creation
    astral construct
    web
    creation
    hail of crystals
    ruin
    rebirth
    create demiplane
    implosion

%^CYAN%^Kineticist:%^RESET%^ 
    animate object
    energy emanation
    energy cone
    hold person
    energy current
    bolt of force
    reddopsi
    crushing hand
    tornado blast

%^CYAN%^Nomad:%^RESET%^
    dimension slide
    phantom steed
    dismissal
    dimensional anchor
    psionic teleport
    planar sending
    planar portal
    astral projection
    timestop

%^CYAN%^Telepath:%^RESET%^ 
    command
    charm monster
    hostile empathic transfer
    modify memory
    domination
    serenity
    visions from within
    mindnet
    overwhelming presence
   

